dnsBenchmark

Run DNS server benchmark against all configured DNS servers. Tests each server with a well-known hostname (google.com) and returns response times sorted from fastest to slowest.

dnsBenchmark(
  deviceId: String!
): DnsBenchmarkResult!

Arguments

dnsBenchmark.deviceIdString! non-null scalar

Device/router ID

Type

DnsBenchmarkResult object

Complete benchmark result comparing all configured DNS servers
